# Drop zone — the folder and its README are tracked, but everything
# else dropped here stays local. The triage workflow reads from this
# folder, moves binaries into Raw/<subfolder>/ (which IS tracked),
# extracts text into typed notes, and leaves the originals untracked.
Inbox/*
!Inbox/README.md

# Obsidian Daily Notes auto-creates these at root; keep them out of git
# so they don't drift into the commit log.
/today.md
/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9].md

# Generated letter artifacts (mail-merged docx, intermediate md) — content is local-only
outputs/**
!outputs/README.md
